reviewText: Another Disney Sing Along Songs video that is great fun for the family. Featuring songs from most of the older Disney classics, this video's main  highlight for me was "Ugly Bug Ball" from Summer Magic, performed by the wonderful actor Burl Ives. Recommended. Good classic Disney sing along fun.

reviewText: We've had the Disney Sing-alongs for a long time and never ordered this.  Now that we finally succumbed, it's a nice addition to the series, but we've discovered that it's not quite the same as the original series volume would have been, so some of the songs are already on other videos we have.  But not much of an overlap, and we do love watching these, so it's fun to have another one.
